&#8216;S1/E2 &#8211; 1/2&#8217;. Aapji initiates negotiations with Saloni&#8217;s family. But they will not hear anything and reiterate that Saloni is already engaged.&#8216;S1/E3 &#8211; 1/3&#8217;. Samar&#8217;s wedding to Kaveri causes a stir and there are consequences. Kaveri tells Saloni that her parents were forcing him to marry someone else to collect money for her dowry.